quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,112,"Ni twansengwasyisye ni abali ja (kum’beleka) Isihaka, Ntume jwa mu ŵandu ŵambone."
  37,113,"Ni twampele upile jwalakwe ni Isihaka jwakwe. Sano mu ŵanache ŵao mwana nkukolosya (itendo yakwe) ni nkulitenda lupuso nsyene mwakuonechela."
  37,114,"Soni chisimu chene twampele ukoto Musa ni Haruna."
  40,55,"Basi pililani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), chisimu chilanga cha Allah chakuonaonape, soni ŵendani chikululuko ku sambi syenu, ni nnuswejesyeje lumbili lwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) kwigulo ni kundaŵi."
  40,56,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakukangana pa ma Ȃya ga Allah mwangali umboni uliose wawayichilile, m’mitima mwao mwangali ikaŵeje kulikwesya, (akusosa ukulu wakumpunda Muhammadi ﷺ) nambo nganaŵa aŵuŵiche ŵanganyao, basi lijuyani mwa Allah, chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakulolechesya."
  40,57,"Chisimu gumba mawunde ni mataka kuŵele kwekulungwa nnope kupunda gumba ŵandu, nambo ŵandu ŵajinji ngaakumanyilila."
  41,34,"Yambone ni yakusakala ngaŵa nkulandana. Tyosyani (yakusakala) ni ayila (itendo) yaili yambone (jwantendele yakusakala mum’buchisyani yambone), basi n’jile sayi ajula jwapali pachilikati penumwe ni jwalakwe pana utinda, taŵe nti chisawu nsyoŵe jwapantima."
  41,35,"Nambo nganaŵa apedwile yalakweyo ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaapiliile, soni nganaŵa apedwile yalakweyo ikaŵeje ajula jwaakwete liunjili lyekulungwa (lya umbone)."
  41,36,"Sano naga achintyosyaga kwene (ku masengo gambone) nkutyosya jwalijose jwachishetani, basi lijuuyaani mwa Allah, chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope."
  42,19,"Allah ni Mpole nnope kwa achikapolo Ŵakwe, akumpaga lisiki jwansachile, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwakulimbangana nnope, Jwamachili gakupunda."
  42,20,"Jwaŵele ali nkusachilila (ni itendo yakwe) malipilo ga ku Akhera, chitukan’jonjechesye pa malipilo gakwe, ni jwaŵele ali nkusachilila (ni itendo yakwe) malipilo ga pa duniya, chitumpe palakwepo (yayannembele kuti impate), ni ngasakola jwalakwejo ku Akhera liunjili lililyose (lya yambone)."
  42,21,"Kapena akwete ŵanganyao akwawanganya (ni Allah), ŵaŵalamulile mu dini yanganachisya Allah, soni lingaŵaga liloŵe lya chilekanganyo (lyalyalongolele kala lyangapa ilagasyo yekulungwa ikaŵeje ku Kiyama), kungaajiilanyidwe chilikati chao, soni chisimu ŵalupuso tachipata ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope."
  43,1,"Hâ. Mîm. ",footnotes:1:[Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.]
  43,2,"Nguchilumbila Chitabu (cha Qur’an) chakusalichisya."
  43,3,"Chisimu Uwwe tujitesile jalakweji kuŵa Qur’an jacharabu kuti jenumanja mpate kugataga mu lunda (mate gakwe chenene)."